name: Red Sweater Block Print Christmas Cards
description:
These Christmas cards are my own art and individually handprinted. They are a traditional yet unique holiday card. The sweater is a cozy winter image. Send a small work of art, not just a card.

Ten Cards and envelopes
Each card is 6.5x5"

name: Christmas Tree Block Print Cards
description:
These beautifully designed cards are little works of art and perfect as a Christmas, New Years or non-denominational cards. Their simplicity and elegance lend a fresh look to the holiday season. The trees are printed in a combination of forest green and gold and each card will vary slightly in coloration. Send a little piece of art this holiday season.

TEN Cards with envelopes
Each card is 6.5x5"

name: Folk Reindeer Illustrated Christmas Cards
description:
This Reindeer Christmas card combines a traditional symbol of the holidays with a fresh interpretation of the motif that mimics folk art. The original art is illustrated with pastels and each print is mounted on a 5 x 6 1/2" white card. The ample card size and simplicity of design packs a visual punch.

10 cards and 10 white envelopes

name: Folk Bird Illustrated Christmas Cards
description:
This Folk Bird Christmas card is printed from my original art and combines a traditional symbol of the holidays with a fresh interpretation of the motif that mimics folk art with a graphic, modern design. The original art is illustrated with pastels and each print is mounted on a 5 x 6 1/2" white card. The ample card size and simplicity of design packs a visual punch. 

Ten cards in a set.

name: 2014 Illustrated Desk Food Calendar
description: Each month of the year is illustrated with a lush still life painting in this desk top calendar. Perfect for the office or kitchen counter. Each page is 4 x 4 inches and the little stand is wood and a 2 inch cube. This set comes with a gift box that is shipped to you flat and easily assembled.
